     H            Y.
     F** UTLR52B ***************************************************
     F*  UTILITY - GET ALLOW SPLIT FLAG IN PACKING LIST OPTION     *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA)  2026.03.11                             *
     F*------------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR52B'
     F*                    PARM           $NONY   4
     F*                    PARM           $MIX    1
     F*   IN  $NONY   4  DELIVERY
     F*   OUT $MIX    1  FLAG (Y/N) FOR ALLOWING SPLIT BY MAX BOX
     F******************************************************
     FAB#PP9A IF  E           K        DISK
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $NONY   4
     C                     PARM           $MIX    1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $MIX
      *
     C           $NONY     SETLLAB#PP9A
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           $NONY     READEAB#PP9A                  98
     C   98                LEAVE
      *
     C           YBSKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVELYBMIX     $MIX
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
